snippet.title: I made an Among Us fangame for the Gameboy Color! (trailer)
snippet.description:
Super Impostor Bros. is a platformer/choose your own adventure game that I'll be releasing for free shortly!
Patreon Pals are currently bugtesting the game: https://www.patreon.com/posts/48730953
Once bugtesting is over, the game will release for everyone!

The Super Imposter Bros. team:
Art: me (LumpyTouch)
Programming/Design: Danee
Music: MelonadeM (She made the Garfield Gameboy'd COMPLETE Credits music)
MelonadeM Twitter: https://twitter.com/_melonadem

🦆Follow me on TWITTER: https://twitter.com/LumpyTouch​​
📷The Lumpy INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/lumpytouch/​​
📺Art Stream on TWITCH: https://www.twitch.tv/lumpytouch​

#trailer #gameboy #amongus
